 Signal Post #2 – FG-411: Cert “Question • Split • Gap” Ladder

🎯 The Supreme Court doesn’t answer every question.

They answer the ones framed just right.
Question → Circuit Split → Legal Gap.

That’s the ladder. Miss a rung, and your cert petition falls.

The Field Guide shows how to climb it.
Because access to justice should not be a guessing game.

